doc.previous: The Eurocopter AS565 Panther is the military version of the Eurocopter AS365 Dauphin medium weight multi purpose twin engine helicopter The Panther is used for a wide range of military roles including combat assault fire support anti submarine warfare anti surface warfare search and rescue and medical evacuation MEDEVAC
